Two of the main function of BPCU are performing power source\Bus transfer and load management coordination. The load management and power transfer are coordinated with other LRUs over redundant communication buses. This project involves Design and development of S/W for Electrical Power Generation System (EPGS) BPCU system. After design, the models are tested for its correct implementation as per the requirements and if they adhere the guidelines mentioned. Later the C code is generated using RTW (Real Time Workshop Embedded Coder). All the requirements in SWDD document are hand coded in C language and integrated with Matlab generated code.
